transcript.speaker: user
transcript.text: I am facing issues with my internet speed today. What do I do?

transcript.speaker: agent
transcript.text: Please power‑cycle your modem and router: turn them off, wait 30 seconds, then turn them back on. After the devices reboot, test your internet speed again.
